---
// Hero
---

<div
  class="hero relative min-h-[200px] md:min-h-[400px] lg:min-h-[600px] flex items-center px-6 md:px-12 py-10 md:py-8 overflow-hidden bg-gradient-to-r from-white via-[#e0f6f6] to-[#4fafb1]"
>
  <!-- Contenedor centrado -->
  <div class="relative z-10 w-full max-w-6xl mx-auto">
    <!-- Texto superpuesto -->
    <div class="pl-0 md:pl-2 ml-1 md:ml-2">
      <!-- Título principal -->
      <h1
        class="font-bold leading-[0.95] tracking-tight mb-1 md:mb-2 overflow-visible"
      >
        <span
          class="font-bold bg-gradient-to-r from-[#2c9b9b] via-[#a1eaec] to-[#c0e6e6] bg-clip-text text-transparent text-[2.5rem] md:text-[3.5rem] lg:text-[4rem] xl:text-[4.5rem] block leading-[1.0]"
        >
          Un legado salesiano:<br />
          educación que transforma vidas
        </span>
      </h1>

      <!-- Subtítulo + Botón -->
      <div class="text-lg md:text-xl lg:text-2xl font-bold bg-gradient-to-r from-[#2c9b9b] via-[#a1eaec] to-[#c0e6e6] bg-clip-text text-transparent space-y-1 mb-10 mt-10"
      >
        <p>Formamos personas</p>
        <p>Íntegras y comprometidas.</p>
        <p>¿Listo para ser parte de nuestra misión?</p>

        <!-- Botón con cursor blanco -->
        <a
          href="#"
          class="inline-block mt-8 ml-4 md:ml-20 lg:ml-40 bg-[#2c9b9b] hover:bg-[#136d6d] text-white text-lg md:text-xl font-semibold py-4 px-8 rounded-lg transition-colors duration-300 transform hover:scale-105 group"
        >
          Admisión 2025
          <img
            src="/images/cursor.svg"
            alt="Cursor"
            class="inline-block ml-2 w-5 h-5 transition-transform duration-300 group-hover:translate-x-1 filter invert brightness-0"
          />
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Imagen decorativa -->
<div
  class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-full lg:top-10 lg:right-0 lg:left-auto lg:h-auto lg:w-1/2 z-0 flex items-center justify-center opacity-100 pointer-events-none"
>
  <img
    src="/images/santos2.jpg"
    alt="Educación Salesiana"
    class="w-full h-full lg:h-full max-h-[80vh] object-cover lg:object-contain object-center lg:object-right rounded-none lg:rounded-[10%/10%]"
    style="
      -webkit-mask-image: radial-gradient(ellipse at center, black 60%, transparent 100%);
      mask-image: radial-gradient(ellipse at center, black 60%, transparent 100%);
      -webkit-mask-repeat: no-repeat;
      mask-repeat: no-repeat;
      -webkit-mask-size: 100% 100%;
      mask-size: 100% 100%;
    "
  />
</div>
</div>